original_title: SKE48 リクエストアワー セットリストベスト30 2010
overview: SKE48 Request Hour Setlist Best 30 2010 ~Kami-kyoku wa dore da?~ was SKE's first solo Request Hour concert. A voting ticket was included in Aozora Kataomoi's Regular Edition and all the songs from S1, S2, S3, KII1, KII2 and single songs including AKB's A-Sides from 10nen Zakura to Sakura no Shiori (Including Majisuka Rock'n'Roll) were available to vote. The Request Hour concert was held on July 31, 2010 at Nagoya International Convention Center, Century Hall.
tagline: Which songs are going to be the Kamikyoku?
title: SKE48 Request Hour Setlist Best 30 2010
